  <summary>4/22/2015--Introduced.
Clean Ocean and Safe Tourism Anti-Drilling Act or the COAST Anti-Drilling Act

 Amends the Outer Continental Shelf Lands Act to prohibit the Secretary of the Interior from issuing a lease or other authorization for the exploration, development, or production of oil, natural gas, or any other mineral in either the Mid-Atlantic, South Atlantic, or the North Atlantic planning areas.</summary>
